      },
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# ✨ Promise\n\nState the sharpest version of what the product changes.\n\nThis is where the product stops sounding like software and starts sounding like a shift in capability."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "product-story-template-difference",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🧭 Why It Exists",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
