        "borderRadius": 24
      },
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# 🧭 Why It Exists\n\nExplain the fracture in the current tool landscape.\n\nWhat is scattered today? What becomes coherent here?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "product-story-template-proof",
